      "text": "save \u0027cut2.json\u0027 with content \u0027{\u0022db\u0022:\u0022plang\u0022,\u0022port\u0022:8080}\u0027",
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Cut 2 \u2014 lazy read \u002B narrow \u002B chain-wide !.\n%file!file!path% resolves location-only (no content read); is file \u2192 true with no read.\n%file.field% reads \u002B parses \u002B narrows; second use stays cached; the facet hop\nstill resolves after the narrow.",
